\par }\pard \nowidctlpar\tx720\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\tqdec\tx9360 {\f5 The Communications Settings Dialog will present different options depending on the type of connection that was chosen in the Session Settings.
\par 
